From Steven Murray Subject Re RAMs ROMs with ALE latches for 's In article qg sINN j pethybridge writes Hello again, I asked this a year ago, but i am still looking I am getting sick of having to use a HC If you are just getting sick of the real estate used by the HCT , you could always use the approach I have seen one designer take he stuck the chip in the middle of the EPROM socket, under the EPROM Naturally, you have to use an IC socket with the right dimensions, but layout is really easy Steven Murray